=== Plugin Name ===
Contributors: mmt@mmt.me.uk
Tags: sharenice, widget, sharing, social
Requires at least: 3.3.1
Tested up to: 3.3.1
Stable tag: 0.2

Adds a sharenice icon to a wordpess

== Description ==

This displays the sharenice.org ethical social sharing widget

== Installation ==

1. Upload the files (sharenice.php, README.TXT) to the `/wp-content/plugins/sharenice` directory
2. Activate the plugin through the 'Appearance -> Widgets' menu in WordPress

